because of that.

00:03:24.036 --> 00:03:25.938
Anyway, but I loved there.

00:03:25.971 --> 00:03:28.874
I got to play Ronald McDonald

00:03:28.907 --> 00:03:30.543
for the kids on Sundays

00:03:30.576 --> 00:03:32.044
