00:03:52.598 --> 00:03:54.433
so when you're giving away
free food.

00:03:54.466 --> 00:03:56.369
And, you know--and by the way,

00:03:56.402 --> 00:03:58.037
all that food
that was in the hopper

00:03:58.070 --> 00:03:59.739
that they put into
