00:05:43.041 --> 00:05:46.712
and you could win a Big Mac
or a Big Breakfast or $5.

00:05:46.745 --> 00:05:49.682
And so, I was getting ready
to leave--it was Friday night.

00:05:49.715 --> 00:05:51.817
