the sides off.

00:06:01.193 --> 00:06:04.563
And in the morning, we had
157 free Big Breakfastes.

00:06:04.596 --> 00:06:06.532
And we'd been up all night with
the free beer.

00:06:06.565 --> 00:06:08.734
And it was, like, a real classy
party,

00:06:08.767 --> 00:06:10.202
like, you know, a brunch of
something,

00:06:10.235 --> 00:06:12.004
so, anyway,
we go down to McDonald's.

00:06:12.037 --> 00:06:13.839
Since I work there,
I can't cash it in.

00:06:13.872 --> 00:06:15.608
But my buddy Moe can.

00:06:15.641 --> 00:06:17.376
So I park behind the dumpster.

00:06:17.409 --> 00:06:19.912
And Moe goes in
and he goes up to the front.

00:06:19.945 --> 00:06:22.114
And he puts them up there
and he says,

00:06:22.147 --> 00:06:25.751
"I'd like
157 free Big Breakfastes."

00:06:25.784 --> 00:06:27.420
And the lady goes,

00:06:27.453 --> 00:06:30.556
"Oh, I'm sorry, sir, did
you not read the fine print?

00:06:30.589 --> 00:06:32.258
It's only one per visit."

00:06:32.291 --> 00:06:34.059
And my friend Moe
is pretty smart.

00:06:34.092 --> 00:06:37.062
He's like,
"Boy, the kids at the home

00:06:37.095 --> 00:06:39.031
